ot;<br />\n<br />\n你想咒自己? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e6b05fa963669354b041fde6da1396cc5fdd2a","tid":368264,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4年一句性格不合898了</blockquote><br />\nx2"},{"pid":"fcb83c441cc5bf250cc61fec55bd09723d1a04c0","tid":368264,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1個月 原因係我發現我唔鐘意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我認我係衰人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">之後俾人用同一個原因挽返轉頭</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">挽你老母</span>"},{"pid":"b13f7e7812bcfa84dfb442d28cb6c4bc34f76c0b","tid":368264,"uid":112692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:00:23.000Z","msg":"1年 但係我覺得會係我人生最難忘既1年<br />\n都應該有6,7年咁耐 但係每次諗返起都好似係昨日發生咁"},{"pid":"9c62073459619054c55a44f5b689629bf50c9f5a","tid":368264,"uid":123663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082c34dc38a209789410c25217f572d01f73bb3c","tid":368264,"uid":123663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:02:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1個月 原因係我發現我唔鐘意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我認我係衰人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">之後俾人用同一個原因挽返轉頭</span></span></blockquote><br />\n可憐剃頭者人亦剃其頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢件事教你要認真對待感情啊巴打，有時可以傷得人好深"},{"pid":"372dc8cfb28210e62c13a368ff59cd525731c9fa","tid":368264,"uid":138618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"4年 佢厭左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6855a1ba72