By":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T20:26:35.000Z","msg":"七年幾 long d左四五年<br />\n都係淡左而分開"},{"pid":"a73b91c7021def07195ff131257fb83359d9750d","tid":368264,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T20:28:29.000Z","msg":"斷斷續續２年，有搵返大家，timing唔岩冇一齊返"},{"pid":"656f1a512513407854872a4b6e1bc46ef013c076","tid":368264,"uid":136572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T20:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三年<br />\n佢發太多脾氣，肯改嘅時候已經太遲</blockquote><br />\nI know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當心淡之後 就算點講想箍煲都真係唔想再回頭<br />\n但可能始終係初戀 所以到分咗手咁耐都唔太放得低<br />\n而且佢嘅任性令到我對拍拖已經無太大信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d6bf1499fde2fa2b0b798c37be3fb9f568132b","tid":368264,"uid":138594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T01:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲一齊緊 拍左9年加新婚8個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 無架 都係大家d性格慢慢磨合 尊重同體諒 同埋真心錫對方 拍下拍下就咁長時間 不過一開始我身邊d fd都睇死我地好快散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n利申 14歲開始拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d9f49ee2903c5294ec1e22d9da620193b6c7c5","tid":368264,"uid":138594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T01:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲一齊緊 拍左9年加新婚8個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n少見啲啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打好幸福</bloc