ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:49:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1個月 原因係我發現我唔鐘意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我認我係衰人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">之後俾人用同一個原因<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">挽</span>返轉頭</span></span></blockquote><br />\n挽你老母先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你唔撚鍾意人真係咪撚柒應撚成鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以宜家好後悔當初唔鐘意人但又同人一適<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我終於明白同一個唔愛你嘅人拍拖再分手係咩感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}